Polynom - Class in myMath
This class represents a Polynom with add, multiply functionality, it also should support the following: 1.
Polynom() - Constructor for class myMath.Polynom
This is default constructor
Polynom(String) - Constructor for class myMath.Polynom
This constructor gets string and cut by "+", and turns it into Polynom Example : 2x^2+2^x+-5
Polynom(Polynom) - Constructor for class myMath.Polynom
This is copy constructor
Polynom_able - Interface in myMath
This interface represents a general Polynom: f(x) = a_1X^b_1 + a_2*X^b_2 ... a_n*Xb_n, where: a_1, a_2 ... a_n are real numbers and b_1=0 are none negative integers (naturals) For formal definitions see: https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Polynomial Such polygon has the following functionality: 1.
